Package: pebble-led
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pebble smartwatch BLE daemon
 Connects to a Pebble smartwatch over Bluetooth Low Energy and runs as a
 user service providing time sync, desktop-notification forwarding, and an
 AppMessage bridge over D-Bus.
 .
 The daemon links libdbus statically; there is no runtime libdbus dependency.
 BlueZ is accessed through the system D-Bus.
